name: Floral Printed Top
description:
A beautiful floral printed asymmetrical sleeveless top from a Japanese label, 'Mysty Woman'. 

A must-have piece for summer to go with earthy tone, shorts and oak leather boots to create a vintage look.

Fabric: Jersey
Colour: Floral Prints in khaki, pale grey and off red.
Size: S/M
Condition: Good
Made: Japan

name: Sleeveless Utility Silk Dress
description:
This lovely Portman silk sleeveless dress comes with a skinny silk waist band in the same tone. 
It can be worn as a dress on its own or with the skinny waist band tied around with the waist at the front or the back to give the body a slender look. It can also be worn with skinny jeans with the collar wide open as a light weight sleeveless trench vast.

A lovely piece that can be worn in several ways.

Fabric: Silk
Color: Black
Size: AU 8 equivalent to a US 4
Condition: Excellent - Only worn once
